data.description: Welcome to 3 Red Bud in Harrisburg! This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, offering a comfortable and spacious living environment. The living room, kitchen, and dining room flow seamlessly, providing an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment. The well-equipped kitchen features a pantry and modern appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. Cozy up by the gas fireplace in the living room during colder evenings. Experience the outdoors in the screened porch, complete with a TV for added enjoyment. Situated on a double lot, this property provides ample outdoor space, including a shed for extra storage. Enjoy privacy and energy efficiency with custom day/night insulating cellular shades. Updates include a new HVAC system, water heater, and garage door opener, ensuring comfort and convenience. The main bath, kitchen, flooring, and appliances have been tastefully updated, creating a contemporary and welcoming atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home with its thoughtful features and recent improvements!
